---
import RegionSection from "./RegionSection.astro";
---

<RegionSection

    title="Overview"

    subtitle="The heartland of Eldoria."

>

    <div class="overview">

        <p>

            Solmara is the largest and most populous region in Eldoria, stretching across vast golden plains, fertile farmlands, and rolling hills. Home to nearly five hundred million people, it has long served as the continent's agricultural and commercial heart.

        </p>

        <p>

            Rather than existing as a single nation, Solmara is composed of numerous independent monarchies, each governing its own lands while maintaining strong relationships through trade, diplomacy, and mutual prosperity. This decentralized structure has allowed diverse kingdoms to flourish while preserving their own traditions and identities.

        </p>

        <p>

            Known for its warm climate, lively festivals, magical innovation, and enduring spirit of freedom, Solmara welcomes travelers from every corner of Eldoria. Whether crossing the ancient Crown Road, studying within Aurelis, or exploring the bustling streets of Valemore, visitors quickly discover why the Golden Heartland remains one of the continent's most beloved regions.

        </p>

    </div>

</RegionSection>

<style>

.overview{

    max-width:900px;

    margin:auto;

    display:flex;

    flex-direction:column;

    gap:2rem;

}

